, and got a few empty saddle bags. Skye stayed home, as she rode out to near by villages to pick up supplies, blankets, tons of rice, extra medicine and other things they all will need.<br>
  She also bought an ax. She thought to herself,&quot; When I get back I should start chopping fire wood so we can keep the children and elderly warm. This winter will be very hard on them the most.&quot;<br>
  As she rode back to Themiscrya, All she had on her mind was how to get revenge on Zeus, Whether she could ever or would ever attempt anything is unknown. She found it unfair that all of them should be punished for a marriage. She didn't blame Hera, for Hera did what she thought was right, But she was a little upset for the consequence that it brought. Sethra, rare to be angry was.&quot;Zeus will pay&quot; she said out loud. &quot;Amazons Unite&quot; as the Queen had said was the only hope that kept her spirits from totally falling::<br>
